About me I'm a Research Engineer at AI System Dept. in DeNA. I engage myself in Research and Development on Computer Vision and Machine Learning. If you see this biography and get interested in me, please contact me. In my free time, I drink with my precious people, get inside the world of books, or travel around the world with my green backpack.
 Interests  Research :
I'm generaly interested in Computer Vision and Machine Learning. For details :
